Time":"2017-03-24","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLCibt7FJPfX3NmQXJgwib4vSzH4KZYdazV7mVIb2T19rMp17IOWPFRtUtw3EGtywx9BBGozp9Lacl6w/0","content":"１、您觉得这个报告中有什么部分是有问题的？\n２、这个报告面向的人是哪些？\n３、您希望这个报告能达到什么样的效果？","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5510,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490358427000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"元气少女\uD83C\uDF3B","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-24","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEtZxnzBwbLAzpTXp5C3ZzUHD4DU6cvkh8OklJNSCZ8mXDhbEV4AggLvNYTNhvP5NdpIVt1D4iajHk/0","content":"1.从侧面看老板需要这份报告呈现什么样的效果\n2.对老板最近焦虑的事情多观察，找到合适的帮助方式写在报告中\n3.确定老板让我写的报告的目的是否和我理解的相同","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5405,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490320514000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"张YY","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-23","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLDC88nCjl5mticEwn6d95CyLS2K9XiaEIPB6n8icXpxKiaNZlVIVbTBj7XJVOQvkuoOHDzbycbc5YU9tA/0","content":"观察老板平时对员工工作的要求及他的个人工作习惯，老板是一个对待工作认真要紧，注重细节的人，报告被打回来的原因可能是细节文字太多，需要推敲矫正。\n可以找老板的秘书寻求帮助，咨询了解自己的报告问题出在哪里了？\n直接找老板指导","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4963,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490234867000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"彭婷A梦","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoIn82IzpZnG2VX4Vic411jI1gE0GRdYOuUu0CFb0ic2szPichkbnC0Eg8VDFT9Zj6FCm6kl0DlHYKJS/0","content":"1、先判断是因为老板自身原因（心情不好导致自己被迁怒，其实报告压根儿没看），还是报告本身存在问题（没做好）导致被要求返工重做。\n2、若是前者，自己观察一下或者侧面向他人询问是不是发生了什么事情。再择时间重新递交报告。\n3、若是后者，\n（1）换位思考一下，如果自己是老板，对方希望看到什么？这份报告背后隐藏的真实诉求是什么？报告数据的背后实际上是显示出了什么问题？对此有没有什么解决对策？\n（2）直接询问老板认为报告是哪里不对。是自己漏了什么方面没有提到，还是一开始报告的调查和写作思路就不对。双方达到一个共同认知点，自己再回去修改。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4562,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490093738000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"俞悦","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLANZo09gQTTkSzvHFqibxNaah02fZMYxmspFkicQSzo8hbBVImPBFbjOkYibjAmt9lUUMaJHNB54hAWw/0","content":"老板，要做这个报告的主要目的是什么呢？还可以通过什么方式来达到这个目的呢？以终为始，我还可以做些什么帮助达到目的呢？","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4587,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490054272000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Pan","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay5KhpQIRIpY7DYXTlcKMicsq47nNJOC9PJu3VFIvUZUn410lK377dOFpG8rWiaoJQia6vpIP3zyVuEV/0","content":"第一步：应该进行理解偏差的梳理；\n   老板需要报告的目的是什么，给什么人看，关注什么样的数据，通过查看报告需要达成什么目的。\n\n第二步：隐藏偏差的梳理；\n    当满足老板声称的需求后，还是被打回来，这时候我们就需要清楚老板背后的诉求了。老板是不是有其他的需求不便于直接表达的。\n    1观察老板对报告中的哪一个数据比较在意\n    2询问同事老板最近有什么样的苦恼，或者面临什么样的冲突。\n    3考虑老板的背景，注意老板的重点是那一部分内容\n    4如果清楚这些以后，考虑是不是需要更改报告中的一部分数据或者内容。如果是不违背原则的是不是可以做其他的东西。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4565,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490027120000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"\uD83D\uDC8DEileen\uD83D\uDD06","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6abalthMJiaYnoibZVuO5CvSR8HOKWNjhJyafcnkmAkvTZ9NZIu7ibtL0hZb0tFft1ZWlJB8cmhjzGuaQSxNldicib3T/0","content":"1，老板原因。老板不爽我，我怎么做他都觉得不好，从平时观察来看，我提交的碰到方案或者提议，他都觉得不好，其他人说都会说好，或者容易得到认可\n2，我理解错老板说的改善会议流程的意思。老板是否因为我理解错您的意思，您所需要的会议流程优化是指人员的优化么？即开会的时候只需要每个部门的最高管理人员参与即可？还是其他呢？\n3，其他地方挖掘。平时多观察老板每次作出的决定背后的原因或者是他在把方案退给你的时候说了什么，特别是不好的方面","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3339,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489829836000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"lizzie","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoBp020iboYUPZIm7Kn1xhUSodfrjYOqZaqpdScptV7c8cPTpxDbJ4b7k8icIOPu9qJ2OCVm5XwibfKk/0","content":"通过和老板沟通交流发掘出老板对这份报告的真实需求\n老板对哪部分不满意，不满意的原因，分析这个原因\n通过和其他报告通过的同事比较，老板不满意的这部分和这些同事的报告差在哪，如果差距比较大则改进，如果差距不大就进一步思考:老板对于这份报告会有什么特殊的要求","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3946,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489806678000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Aven","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoEHiaTBylWfkP5h3Gr8mVTk7y1OoguaVia4gbQH9po2STdmlDDRIh5M8Q6HKX1ZibryxePwyZWq1Onc/0","content":"1、直接提问需求。2、发现老板做的原因与目的。3、给老板提供多种方案选择。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3938,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489805004000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"黄小鱼","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoFYKcMqwPWwwvPSNQFxmfw1h1dMGfRjpYERMGP3IelbPWYJgibxcmib3iae2Do6xNrybh5PR3f2YsNa/0","content":"-老板，您觉得这个报告不好的地方在哪呢？\n-公司的研究不透彻\n-老板，您是觉得公司研究哪里不透彻？我已经分析了公司的主营业务、财务情况、竞争格局和竞争优势\n-你这个商业模式没有搞清楚，我们是要搞清楚公司的商业模式去考虑公司是否具有投资价值\n-喔，原来老板的目的是看公司是否具有投资价值。这时候要重点分析公司的商业模式，市场的天花板，是否具有行业壁垒和估值是否合理。","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3621,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489759253000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Jill Ling","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyyZN53g2CvLEGicxZ4heLHooiaCVwibvbcw8BcDsxgL2AMj3bgU2wNX8OPexCoDeHxKxE9KicExhXd1G/0","content":"1。用5w1h自问自答挖掘老板的目的\nwhy - 为什么要做这个报告？\nwho - 这个报告需要给谁看？\nwhat - 这个报告需要呈现什么信息？以什么样的形式？\nwhen - 这个报告需要包含什么时段的信心？老板什么时候要用？\nhow -  这个报告里的信息要如何呈现？\n\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3575,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489741403000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"新悦","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcKuPUVAWGIRxAVo4SkNmEc9bGP9bCibGTSef90ZbzXj36qdNpqdrRH6LOJCquviaiaicVoqk7bwsJm8RqNY3dwRkjiaC/0","content":"为什么需要重做？\n您觉得这个方案哪里不好？\n是什么原因导致这份方案需要重做？\n您希望这份报告是什么样子的？您希望重新做的报告以什么方式体现？\n您所想的报告都包含哪些部分，通过这份报告想达到什么目的？","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3537,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489729897000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"肖竹","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-16","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLD59UCXXaKTUtCEG9o0icohtHzK8T6MNlTKeyIANBf0tBvzpDtzbWvYOGa2wgDvGdG6k1pCFiafpDjg/0","content":"1.向秘书等老板身边的人（老板的朋友圈等）了解最近老板参加了哪些会议，发生了什么事情，尤其是老板不满意的；\n2.直接向老板提问：我们会议流程中您发现的最主要的问题是什么？或通过与老板关系好的人旁敲侧击地问。\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3400,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489679900000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"影子（one life one liver）","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-16","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay7P6qrmu6EFgMxv9yByicqqSVMrdaJoMs4TEyich23rD3ictMbhBfngbwia0x0G3qzXEM5ib5SQ8bx5vQ/0","content":"第一，老板是在什么样的背景下要求改善会议流程的？澄清了这个问题我就知道，老板他要改善流程的动机是什么？\n第二，他期望通过改善流程的实现什么样的效果？\n\n根据上面两个问题需要考虑的问题是：改善会议流程是解决这个问题的唯一方法吗？有没有其它更好的办法来实现？","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3399,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489679600000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"奔出柵欄的\uD83D\uDC37","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-16","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/